#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.25:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Bhāravagga"
msgstr "3. The Burden"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Chandarāgasutta"
msgstr "25. Desire and Greed"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.25:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.2"
msgid "“Yo, bhikkhave, rūpasmiṃ chandarāgo taṃ pajahatha."
msgstr "“Mendicants, give up desire and greed for form."

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ "
"anabhāvaṃkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhammaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Thus that form will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm "
"stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future."

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.4"
msgid "Yo vedanāya chandarāgo taṃ pajahatha."
msgstr "Give up desire and greed for feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ sā vedanā pahīnā bhavissati ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṃkatā "
"āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.6"
msgid "Yo saññāya chandarāgo taṃ pajahatha."
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.7"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ sā saññā pahīnā bhavissati ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṃkatā "
"āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.8"
msgid "Yo saṅkhāresu chandarāgo taṃ pajahatha."
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.9"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ te saṅkhārā pahīnā bhavissanti ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā "
"anabhāvaṃkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.10"
msgid "Yo viññāṇasmiṃ chandarāgo taṃ pajahatha."
msgstr "consciousness."

msgctxt "sn22.25:1.11"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ taṃ viññāṇaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ "
"anabhāvaṃkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhamman”ti."
msgstr ""
"Thus that consciousness will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a "
"palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.25:1.12"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
